body:
In the code below, REDEFMACRO pragma inside code has no effect. Using it in command-line as -Wno-REDEFMACRO works. 

```verilog
/* verilator lint_off REDEFMACRO */
`define EX 1
/* verilator lint_off REDEFMACRO */
`define EX 0

module m;
  reg a;
  reg [4:0] abcd;
  initial begin
    /* verilator lint_off WIDTHTRUNC */
    a = abcd;
    $finish(2);
  end
endmodule

```

What 'verilator --version' are you using?  Did you try it with the git master version?

Verilator 5.019 devel rev UNKNOWN.REV

What OS and distribution are you using?

WSL

May we assist you in trying to fix this in Verilator yourself?

Yes please!
